# External Integrations

**Analysis Date:** 2026-01-09

## APIs & External Services

**BONKbot Web Terminal API (Primary Data Source):**
- Purpose: Token market data, OHLCV, trades, whale tracking
- SDK/Client: Custom `ApiClient` class in `src/api/client.ts`
- Base URLs:
  - Local: `http://localhost:8787` (development)
  - Beta: `https://beta-data.bonkbot.io/data` (fallback)
- Timeout: 30 seconds (configurable)
- Auth: None (internal service)

**Endpoints Used:**
- `GET /local-api/market_data/{mint}` - Single token market data
- `GET /local-api/market_data_batch?mint=...` - Batch market data
- `GET /local-api/ohlcv/token/{mint}/{resolution}` - Candlestick data
- `GET /local-api/trades/{mint}` - Recent trades
- `GET /local-api/holders_stats/{mint}` - Holder statistics
- `GET /local-api/discovery/whale_moves` - Whale activity
- `GET /local-api/discovery/trending` - Trending tokens
- `GET /local-api/search?text=...` - Token search
- `GET /health` - Health check

## Data Storage

**Databases:**
- None - File-based storage only

**File Storage:**
- Config: `.autopilot/config.json` - `src/config/store.ts`
- Trades: `.autopilot/trades.json` - `src/trading/paper-tracker.ts`
- Location: Project root `.autopilot/` directory (gitignored)

**Caching:**
- In-memory rotation cache per token - `src/rules/rotations.ts`
- No persistent cache

## Authentication & Identity

**Auth Provider:**
- None - Local CLI tool, no user auth

**OAuth Integrations:**
- None

## Monitoring & Observability

**Error Tracking:**
- Console.error for errors
- No external error tracking service

**Analytics:**
- None

**Logs:**
- Console output only
- Bracketed module prefixes: `[WS]`, `[API]`

## CI/CD & Deployment

